rows.label: qev060603_MSG0001
rows.name:
Wait, Vera. I want to be your friend. *fsssh*
Why do you insist on rejecting me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0002
rows.name:
I told you before, I can't stand the idea of someone
living their life as a slave to a duty foisted on them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0003
rows.name:
I can't laugh and smile and pretend it doesn't bother
me that you're wasting your life, because it does.
Please try to understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0004
rows.name:
*fsssh* But that is my nature and destiny as
a Zaruboggan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0005
rows.name:
Yet I still find you very favorable. *fsssh*
Enough to make me want to devoltanize.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0006
rows.name:
What do you mean by favorable?
And what the heck does "devoltanize" mean?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0007
rows.name:
Look, you don't know anything about me. And you...
I'm sorry, but you're too clingy. It's annoying![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060603_MSG0009
rows.name: Good-bye, Orleron. Don't come around here again.[ST:wait ]
